Package controller.ProfileControllers

Class HomeLocationController

java.lang.Object
controller.BaseControllers.Controller
controller.BaseControllers.MainAppController
controller.ProfileControllers.HomeLocationController
public class HomeLocationController extends MainAppController
Controller of the home address map. Used to set the address during registration and allows users to change their address later in their profile. Uses an html of the map and a js for the actions on the map.
